--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>
 As I stood on a wind-swept hill, watching the sun rise, I sighed, longing to join my blade with others in battle, and yet not knowing where I might find adventurers in need of me. Below me, on the shores of the great ocean, a woodelf ranger and a troll did battle together against a common foe. The sight disturbed me. <br>
<br>
And then a voice called to me on the wind. Isharra's lilting tones wound their way with leaves and scents from far away. &quot;A Call to Arms!&quot; she cried. &quot;A Call to Arms for those good of heart and those who seek the balance and freedom of neutrality. Join us and find your place among the adventurers you seek!&quot;<br>
<br>
((/ooc Some folks are trying to start up a channel in which to find groups among good/neutral folk. I whole-heartedly support this and hope folks will give it a try. It may help us to keep our beliefs and find adventure at the same time. Join channel calltoarms if you seek this.))<br>
<br>
--Mixxi Moondreamer <br>
Halfling champion in the service of Brell<br>
